    "slug": "ai-qr-codes-explained",
    "title": "AI QR Codes: Beautiful Codes That People Actually Scan",
    "description": "Forget boring black-and-white squares. Learn how AI is transforming QR codes into works of art that boost engagement.",
    "date": "2026-01-18",
    "author": "Go2 Team",
    "authorImage": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?w=200&h=200&fit=crop",
    "authorBio": "Making QR codes beautiful, one scan at a time.",
    "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1620712943543-bcc4688e7485?w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&q=80",
