    "content": "\nIf you're using Bitly and feeling the squeeze — higher prices, limited features, slow support — you're not alone. Thousands of marketers, creators, and businesses are looking for alternatives.\n\nThe good news? Switching is easier than you think.\n\n## Why People Are Leaving Bitly\n\nWe hear the same things over and over:\n\n**\"It's getting expensive.\"** Bitly's free tier is limited to 10 links per month now. Want basic analytics? That's $35/month. Need more features? You're looking at $300+/year.\n\n**\"It feels slow.\"** Bitly redirects take around 100ms. That might seem fast, but it's actually 10x slower than it could be.\n\n**\"Support is frustrating.\"** AI chatbots. Endless knowledge base articles. Good luck talking to a human.\n\n**\"The interface is cluttered.\"** What should be simple feels complicated. Finding what you need takes too many clicks.\n\n## What You Get with Go2\n\nHere's what changes when you switch:\n\n| Feature | Bitly | Go2 |\n|---------|-------|-----|\n| Free links | 10/month | 25/month |\n| Basic analytics | Paid ($35/mo) | Free |\n| Custom domains | Paid | Free (1 included) |\n| Redirect speed | ~100ms | ~10ms |\n| QR codes | Basic | AI-generated designs |\n| Retargeting pixels | No | Yes (all plans) |\n| Conversion tracking | No | Yes |\n| Open source | No | Yes |\n\n## The One-Click Migration\n\nWe built a migration tool that makes switching painless:\n\n1. **Connect your Bitly account** — Enter your API key and we'll fetch everything\n2. **Preview your links** — See exactly what will be imported\n3. **Click import** — All your links, tags, and settings come over\n4. **Done** — Your links work immediately\n\nThe whole process takes about a minute. Your old Bitly links keep working (we just copy everything), so there's zero risk of broken links.\n\n### We Also Import From\n\n- Rebrandly\n- Short.io\n- TinyURL\n- Dub.co\n\nSame easy process for all of them.\n\n## What About My Existing Links?\n\nGreat question. Here's how it works:\n\n**Your Bitly links stay active.** We don't touch them. They'll keep working forever (or until Bitly changes something).\n\n**New Go2 links are created.** You get fresh Go2 links with all your existing settings — custom slugs, tags, destinations.\n\n**Gradual transition.** Update links at your own pace. Use Go2 for new campaigns while old links still work.\n\n## The Real Difference\n\nBeyond features and pricing, there's something more fundamental:\n\n**We're transparent.** Go2 is open source. You can see our code, understand how it works, and even self-host if you want. No black boxes.\n\n**We respect privacy.** No cookies tracking your visitors. No selling data. Just clean, ethical link tracking.\n\n**We're fast.** Not \"fast enough\" — actually fast. 10ms redirects mean your visitors get where they're going instantly.\n\n## Ready to Switch?\n\nHere's how to get started:\n\n1. [Create your free Go2 account](/register)\n2. Go to Settings → Migration\n3. Connect your Bitly account\n4. Click \"Import All\"\n\nThat's it. Your links, your brand, your way — just faster, cheaper, and more transparent.\n\n---\n\n*Have questions about migrating? [Contact us](/contact) and a real human will help you.*\n",
